{"tid":1841681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"300人荔枝角集會 與還柙手足團年","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T12:22:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2ab16771a4f41abb1ba8c8ecbe571e4f1b4ae9","tid":1841681,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/GC3IQYKWMA7ZDJ3KISWUMQUQNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FGC3IQYKWMA7ZDJ3KISWUMQUQNU%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6541d0fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FGC3IQYKWMA7ZDJ3KISWUMQUQNU%2F&h=f4401c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/GC3IQYKWMA7ZDJ3KISWUMQUQNU/</a><br />\n<br />\n300人荔枝角集會 與還柙手足團年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200125/large/1579887817_2d5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579887817_2d5d.gif&h=208304e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾300人昨晚在荔枝角收押所外高舉手機燈光，聲援還柙抗爭者。梁志永攝<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】逾300人昨晚響應銀髮族呼籲，年卅晚到荔枝角收押所外「和你團年」，聲援一眾還柙的抗爭者。現場人士舉起手機燈照向收押所，又大喊口號「撐手足撐到底」。聲援者表示，手足比一切更重要，即使不吃團年飯也要來聲援，希望抗爭者知道港人沒有忘記他們。有移民港人回港特意前來，「睇到人心始終離唔開公義同民主，呢班後生仔付出沉重代價，我哋付出嗰少少，其實好濕碎」。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚8時半，荔枝角收押所外聚集大批人群。現場人士舉起手機燈照向收押所，並將多個喇叭朝向收押所，高聲唱歌，又大喊口號「撐手足撐到底」，希望將聲音傳到同伴耳中。<span style=\"color: orange;\">60多歲羅先生表示，除夕夜無法在家舒服地食團年飯，故專誠前來聲援。他說相比起年輕人，「我哋嘅付出根本係微不足道」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港移民：美囚犯不齒港警暴<br />\n<br />\n移民美國港人Raymond帶同孫兒到場聲援，他今次回港兩星期，特意抽空來參與，<span style=\"color: orange;\"></span>。他在美國常常通宵看直播，「成晚唔安樂，見到後生仔俾差人打，佢哋都係為咗自由」。其妻子Anita在美國德州的監獄工作，她對藍絲常說「美國警察仲暴力啦」嗤之以鼻，「啲囚犯都同我講，你睇吓你鄉下啲警察咁樣打人呀」。她稱美國人有槍，所以警察有時要提高武力，「<span style=\"color: orange;\">但係我哋手無寸鐵，佢都可以開槍打啲細路，我真係接受唔到</span>，我以前好proud of我自己I am from Hong Kong，但自從去年6月我係so shame！」<span style=\"color: orange;\">到場叫口號李同學則說，手足比一切更重要，即使不吃團年飯都要來聲援。</span><br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200125/large/1579887817_766b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579887817_766b.gif&h=13d7cb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有銀髮族向收押所方向吶喊，希望手足知道沒被遺忘。<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝銀髮族沒有遺忘為大家付出的年輕人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0598c0f3e39324227d0fdefc02757c00860b9b55","tid":1841681,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"898f46c124a1c443690d39fc5cb7f149bb0acd6c","tid":1841681,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee528797fa1067e06292728db6935b35d31daf32","tid":1841681,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"